text: Wrong address on shipping label. Package sent to 123 Oak Street instead of 123 Elm Street. Different neighborhood entirely.

Parcel weighing 15 lbs dispatched from Dallas warehouse. Tracking stuck on 'in-transit' for 8 business days.
